SIALKOT, Feb 2 (APP):Special Assistant to Prime Minister on Information and Broadcasting Dr Firdous Ashiq Awan held an open court in Koobey Chak village near here on Sunday.
The SAPM listened to the problems and complaints of people and issued orders for their early relief, compliance and redressal.
